x_t, t \in \{0,\Delta t, 2\Delta t,\ldots,T-\Delta t,T\}
\dot x_t
\dot x_t = \frac{x_t-x_{t-1}}{\Delta t}
\dot x_t = \frac{x_{t+1}-x_t}{\Delta t}
\ddot x_t = \frac{\dot x_{t+1}-\dot x_t}{\Delta t}
\ddot x_t = \frac{\dot x_t-\dot x_{t-1}}{\Delta t}
\Delta t
\dot{x}_t = \frac{x_{t+1} - x_{t-1}}{2 \Delta t}
O(\Delta t)^2
O(\Delta t)
\ddot{x}_t = \frac{x_{t+1} - 2 x_t + x_{t-1}}{(\Delta t)^2}
\Delta t
x_{t+1}
x_s
